    "description": "Judofuri is a local party game from 2 to 9 players, where you face off in a variety of easy-to-pickup, fast-paced mini-games. Bring your friends and family and embrace the chaos!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227940/extras/GIF_Assemble-compressed.gif?t=1728042294\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONE BUTTON ONLY</strong></h2>Each player needs one, and ONLY one button to compete in Judofuri. And you get to choose yours at the beginning of each session! A mouse click, a gamepad trigger, a spacebar, anything works. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227940/extras/GIFOneButton-compressed.gif?t=1728042294\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>20+ MINI-GAMES</strong></h2>Race through hurdles, chop vegetables, train your cardio, fish, and more! Each mini-game is unique and requires a different skill, so everyone gets their opportunity to shine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227940/extras/GIF_Minigames.gif?t=1728042294\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SHARE THE CONTROLLER</strong></h2>Tired of always being one gamepad short for your couch gaming sessions? Share the same device with 2, 3, even 9 players!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227940/extras/GIFShareController-compressed.gif?t=1728042294\" /></span>",
